duties_responsibilities.duty: Ensure accurate and timely order fulfillment, including picking, packing, and shipping products to exceed customer expectations.
Verify order accuracy, quantity, quality, and expiration dates of items to maintain high standards of service.
Efficiently operate warehouse equipment and machinery, including scanners and packaging tools, to maintain a safe and organized warehouse environment.
Adhere to company safety guidelines, procedures, and regulatory compliance when handling hazardous materials, prescription drugs, and pesticides.
Transact all business in accordance with company's code of ethics and conduct, aligning with the organization's purpose, vision, and values statement.

education_certification.credential: High School diploma or GED preferred
